@page "/tutorial"
<div class="container-fluid min-vh-100" style="background-color: #13131a; color: white; padding: 50px 15px;">
    <h1 class="text-center mb-4" style="color: white;">Exceptional Services for an Unforgettable Stay at GuestGuardian Hotel</h1>
    <p class="text-center mb-5" style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7); font-size: 1.2rem;">Explore our tutorials on various programming languages and tools</p>

    <div class="row">
        <!-- C++ -->
        <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 mb-4">
            <div class="text-center p-4 shadow" style="background-color: #2c2c39; border-radius: 70px;">
                <img src="/Images/TutorialImages/C++.png" alt="C++_Image" class="img-fluid mb-3" style="max-height: 100px;" />
                <h3 style="color: white;">C++</h3>
                <p style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);">"Powerful and versatile, C++ combines object-oriented programming with high-performance capabilities. Ideal for system-level programming, game development, and resource-intensive applications."</p>
                <button class="btn" style="background-color: #4e4e7e; color: white; border: none; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 5px;">Explore more</button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- C# -->
        <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 mb-4">
            <div class="text-center p-4 shadow" style="background-color: #2c2c39; border-radius: 70px;">
                <img src="/Images/TutorialImages/CSharp.png" alt="C#_Image" class="img-fluid mb-3" style="max-height: 100px;" />
                <h3 style="color: white;">C#</h3>
                <p style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);">"Modern and robust, C# powers everything from Windows applications to game development with Unity. Designed for productivity and performance."</p>
                <button class="btn" style="background-color: #4e4e7e; color: white; border: none; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 5px;">Explore more</button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- HTML -->
        <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 mb-4">
            <div class="text-center p-4 shadow" style="background-color: #2c2c39; border-radius: 70px;">
                <img src="/Images/TutorialImages/html.png" alt="HTML_Image" class="img-fluid mb-3" style="max-height: 100px;" />
                <h3 style="color: white;">HTML</h3>
                <p style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);">"The backbone of the web, HTML structures the content you see online. Simple yet essential, it’s the starting point for every website and application."</p>
                <button class="btn" style="background-color: #4e4e7e; color: white; border: none; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 5px;">Explore more</button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Python -->
        <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 mb-4">
            <div class="text-center p-4 shadow" style="background-color: #2c2c39; border-radius: 70px;">
                <img src="/Images/TutorialImages/CSharp.png" alt="Python_Image" class="img-fluid mb-3" style="max-height: 100px;" />
                <h3 style="color: white;">Python</h3>
                <p style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);">"Simple yet powerful, Python is the language for rapid development and versatility. From AI to web development, it’s the go-to for beginners and experts alike."</p>
                <button class="btn" style="background-color: #4e4e7e; color: white; border: none; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 5px;">Explore more</button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Java -->
        <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 mb-4">
            <div class="text-center p-4 shadow" style="background-color: #2c2c39; border-radius: 70px;">
                <img src="/Images/TutorialImages/CSharp.png" alt="Java_Image" class="img-fluid mb-3" style="max-height: 100px;" />
                <h3 style="color: white;">Java</h3>
                <p style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);">"Write once, run anywhere—Java's platform independence makes it a staple for enterprise applications. Reliable, secure, and built for scalability."</p>
                <button class="btn" style="background-color: #4e4e7e; color: white; border: none; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 5px;">Explore more</button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- JavaScript -->
        <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 mb-4">
            <div class="text-center p-4 shadow" style="background-color: #2c2c39; border-radius: 70px;">
                <img src="/Images/TutorialImages/CSharp.png" alt="JavaScript_Image" class="img-fluid mb-3" style="max-height: 100px;" />
                <h3 style="color: white;">JavaScript</h3>
                <p style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);">"The language of the web—JavaScript brings interactivity to life. Essential for front-end development and increasingly dominant in back-end with Node.js."</p>
                <button class="btn" style="background-color: #4e4e7e; color: white; border: none; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 5px;">Explore more</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
